Xin Baicao.

584
00:34:17,440 --> 00:34:18,600
If you call me that again,

585
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:20,240
I'll knock you out

586
00:34:20,240 --> 00:34:21,080
with my spear.

587
00:34:24,160 --> 00:34:25,440
The herbs you want are here.

588
00:34:25,560 --> 00:34:26,280
You can take a look.

589
00:34:35,880 --> 00:34:37,480
You have a talent for studying medicine.

590
00:34:38,000 --> 00:34:39,160
You gathered the exactly right herbs.

591
00:34:40,200 --> 00:34:41,440
Now, brew the broth

592
00:34:42,720 --> 00:34:43,880
using the prescription I gave you.

593
00:34:44,080 --> 00:34:44,640
What?

594
00:34:51,240 --> 00:34:52,520
I gathered the herbs.

595
00:34:52,840 --> 00:34:53,880
And now, I have to brew it on my own.

596
00:34:54,480 --> 00:34:56,000
I am the most hardworking patient
in this world.

597
00:34:56,120 --> 00:34:57,200
Did you pay me?

598
00:34:57,280 --> 00:34:57,720
No.

599
00:34:58,000 --> 00:34:58,720
Then,

600
00:34:58,720 --> 00:34:59,960
you have to brew the medicine yourself.

601
00:35:00,240 --> 00:35:01,320
Do it yourself.

602
00:35:09,280 --> 00:35:10,960
Is there even carrier pigeon
in the Drug King Valley?

603
00:35:15,240 --> 00:35:16,200
Of course.

604
00:35:16,640 --> 00:35:17,680
But this missive

605
00:35:18,800 --> 00:35:19,680
is for you.

606
00:35:20,200 --> 00:35:21,080
For me?

607
00:35:27,160 --> 00:35:29,520
"Are you still alive, Sikong Changfeng?"

608
00:35:30,800 --> 00:35:32,120
How straightforward.

609
00:35:33,720 --> 00:35:34,800
"If you're alive,

610
00:35:35,120 --> 00:35:36,600
don't meet me at Qiandong City.

611
00:35:36,920 --> 00:35:37,920
I left for Tianqi City.

612
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:40,520
Do drop by one day
to try my new liquor."

613
00:35:44,040 --> 00:35:44,480
That's all?

614
00:35:45,280 --> 00:35:46,520
What an interesting person.

615
00:35:46,600 --> 00:35:47,200
Who is he?

616
00:35:47,720 --> 00:35:48,320
Well,

617
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:50,800
he's the man I told you about.

618
00:35:51,480 --> 00:35:54,040
He's Marquis of Zhenxi's only grandson,
Baili Dongjun.

619
00:35:55,200 --> 00:35:56,000
But why

620
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:57,400
did he leave Qiandong City this soon?

621
00:35:58,160 --> 00:35:59,040
I thought his family

622
00:35:59,240 --> 00:36:00,760
didn't allow him to go to Tianqi City?

623
00:36:01,720 --> 00:36:03,000
He didn't explain anything
in the missive.

624
00:36:03,680 --> 00:36:04,440
It seems

625
00:36:04,920 --> 00:36:06,160
you care a lot about him.

626
00:36:06,360 --> 00:36:07,520
Of course.

627
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:09,120
He's a good friend of mine.

628
00:36:10,200 --> 00:36:10,760
All right.

629
00:36:11,320 --> 00:36:12,680
Once you inherit half of my knowledge,

630
00:36:13,000 --> 00:36:14,400
you may head to Tianqi City.

631
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,160
Young people

632
00:36:16,680 --> 00:36:17,960
all want to head there.

633
00:36:18,200 --> 00:36:19,800
In fact, everyone should
visit there once.

634
00:36:20,080 --> 00:36:21,800
It's a city full of talents.

635
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,080
It's also a place

636
00:36:23,120 --> 00:36:24,400
where the young
make a name for themselves.

637
00:36:25,280 --> 00:36:26,560
Does that mean

638
00:36:27,200 --> 00:36:28,400
you too went to Tianqi City

639
00:36:28,920 --> 00:36:29,920
when you were young?

640
00:36:36,880 --> 00:36:38,120
Back then,

641
00:36:39,040 --> 00:36:39,960
the Emperor fell sick.

642
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:41,800
No one from the Imperial Academy
of Medicine could cure him.

643
00:36:41,960 --> 00:36:43,640
Within three days,
more than ten physicians were killed.

644
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:45,680
My master sent me to treat him.

645
00:36:46,000 --> 00:36:47,520
Inside the chamber
was a near-death emperor.

646
00:36:47,720 --> 00:36:48,280
Outside

647
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:50,040
was arms-wielding guards

648
00:36:50,040 --> 00:36:51,440
ready to drag me out and decapitate me.

649
00:36:51,720 --> 00:36:53,080
But my hand with an acupuncture needle
inside it

650
00:36:53,600 --> 00:36:54,680
did not tremble.

651
00:36:55,400 --> 00:36:57,080
I cured the Emperor.

652
00:36:57,760 --> 00:36:58,480
And I said,

653
00:36:59,280 --> 00:37:00,560
as long as the person still breathed,

654
00:37:00,960 --> 00:37:01,920
I could

655
00:37:02,600 --> 00:37:03,440
heal him.

656
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:05,960
Interesting.

657
00:37:09,080 --> 00:37:09,480
I will

658
00:37:10,240 --> 00:37:11,440
head to Tianqi City too.

659
00:37:53,200 --> 00:37:54,560
Do you know why

660
00:37:54,560 --> 00:37:55,800
he refused to sit inside here?

661
00:37:57,280 --> 00:37:58,600
Didn't he explain already?

662
00:37:59,000 --> 00:38:00,000
He's made a pact with someone

663
00:38:00,600 --> 00:38:02,080
to admire the landscape

664
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:03,240
on the journey.

665
00:38:03,480 --> 00:38:05,120
Really?

666
00:38:05,120 --> 00:38:06,440
You actually believe that?

667
00:38:06,760 --> 00:38:07,640
Isn't it obvious?

668
00:38:08,120 --> 00:38:08,760
Imagine.

669
00:38:09,000 --> 00:38:10,080
You came all the way

670
00:38:10,080 --> 00:38:11,080
from Tianqi City

671
00:38:11,080 --> 00:38:11,760
to arrest his master.

672
00:38:11,760 --> 00:38:13,120
And now, his master is dead.

673
00:38:13,120 --> 00:38:14,040
Naturally, he'll put

674
00:38:14,040 --> 00:38:14,960
the blame on you.

675
00:38:17,160 --> 00:38:18,600
In a way,

676
00:38:18,600 --> 00:38:20,480
you're the reason
why his master died.

677
00:38:20,600 --> 00:38:21,800
Arresting his master

678
00:38:22,480 --> 00:38:24,280
and his master's passing

679
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:27,120
are two different things.

680
00:38:28,000 --> 00:38:29,520
If he cannot distinguish them,

681
00:38:29,720 --> 00:38:30,560
then he isn't

682
00:38:30,560 --> 00:38:31,520
who I'm looking for,

683
00:38:31,880 --> 00:38:32,920
nor is he the disciple

684
00:38:33,040 --> 00:38:34,240
Master has been looking for.

685
00:38:35,800 --> 00:38:36,440
Fine.

686
