698
00:39:22,960 --> 00:39:23,920
When I was little,

699
00:39:25,080 --> 00:39:26,160
I thought Qiandong City was huge.

700
00:39:26,960 --> 00:39:27,920
That I could never see every part of it.

701
00:39:28,960 --> 00:39:29,960
When I grew up, I thought

702
00:39:30,600 --> 00:39:31,400
Qiandong City

703
00:39:31,400 --> 00:39:32,240
wasn't that big.

704
00:39:32,960 --> 00:39:34,160
Travel half a day on horseback

705
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:35,520
and you'll see everything.

706
00:39:36,720 --> 00:39:37,640
And now,

707
00:39:38,880 --> 00:39:40,120
I truly feel
that Qiandong City is small.

708
00:39:41,120 --> 00:39:42,400
It's so small that if I venture further,

709
00:39:43,200 --> 00:39:44,200
I won't see it again.

710
00:39:47,440 --> 00:39:48,120
Then...

711
00:39:49,600 --> 00:39:50,960
Did you bid
your parents farewell properly?

712
00:39:52,880 --> 00:39:54,320
They refused to see me.

713
00:39:54,960 --> 00:39:57,120
They said they'd only greet me

714
00:39:57,120 --> 00:39:58,080
