721
00:40:10,440 --> 00:40:12,440
Your grandfather is indeed heroic.

722
00:40:13,760 --> 00:40:15,120
But I won't ask him to do that.

723
00:40:15,600 --> 00:40:16,800
That would be rebellion, right?

724
00:40:18,680 --> 00:40:19,400
Therefore,

725
00:40:19,720 --> 00:40:20,760
I'll take care of myself

726
00:40:21,120 --> 00:40:22,120
in Tianqi City.

